261
00:34:35.909 --> 00:34:37.369
You fuckin' beauty.

262
00:34:48.338 --> 00:34:49.631
Fucking A.

263
00:34:49.714 --> 00:34:51.967
Years of research
just destroyed.

264
00:34:52.133 --> 00:34:53.551
